{"html":"<br/>\n<h2>Fact Symbols with Injective Instances</h2><br/>\n<p class=\"monospace rules\">Server(id,=,.), Y_counter(id,&lt;)</p><br/>\n<h2>Multiset Rewriting Rules</h2><br/>\n<p class=\"monospace rules\"><span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> AC) isend:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> !KU( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> K( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> In( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> AC) irecv:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Out( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">--&gt;</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> !KD( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) BuyANewYubikey:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Fr( ~k ), Fr( ~pid ), Fr( ~sid ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> Protocol( ), Init( ~pid, ~k ), ExtendedInit( ~pid, ~sid, ~k )<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;!Y( ~pid, ~sid ), Y_counter( ~pid, &#39;1&#39; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Server( ~pid, ~sid, &#39;1&#39; ), !SharedKey( ~pid, ~k ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Out( ~pid )<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) Yubikey_Plugin:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Y_counter( pid, sc ), In( sc ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> Yubi( pid, (&#39;1&#39;++sc) ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Y_counter( pid, (&#39;1&#39;++sc) ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">// loop breaker: [0]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) Yubikey_PressButton:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;!Y( pid, sid ), Y_counter( pid, tc ), !SharedKey( pid, k ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;In( tc ), Fr( ~npr ), Fr( ~nonce )<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;YubiPress( pid, tc ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;YubiOTP( pid, senc(&lt;sid, tc, ~npr&gt;, k) ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;YubiSid( pid, sid, k )<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Y_counter( pid, (&#39;1&#39;++tc) ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Out( &lt;pid, ~nonce, senc(&lt;sid, tc, ~npr&gt;, k)&gt; )<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">// loop breaker: [1]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) Server_ReceiveOTP_NewSession:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Server( pid, sid, otc ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;In( &lt;pid, nonce, senc(&lt;sid, tc, ~pr&gt;, k)&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;!SharedKey( pid, k ), In( otc )<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;Login( pid, sid, tc, senc(&lt;sid, tc, ~pr&gt;, k) ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;LoginCounter( pid, otc, tc ), Smaller( otc, tc )<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Server( pid, sid, tc ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">// loop breaker: [0]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span></p><br/>\n<h2>Restrictions of the Set of Traces</h2><br/>\n<p class=\"monospace rules\"><span class=\"hl_keyword\">restriction</span> smaller:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;<span class=\"hl_operator\">∀ </span>#i a b<span class=\"hl_operator\">.</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>Smaller( a, b ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">@</span> #i<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">⇒</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span><span class=\"hl_operator\">∃ </span>z<span class=\"hl_operator\">.</span> (a++z) <span class=\"hl_operator\">=</span> b<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span>&quot;<br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/*<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;expanded formula:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;<span class=\"hl_operator\">∀ </span>#i a b<span class=\"hl_operator\">.</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>Smaller( a, b ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">@</span> #i<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">⇒</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span><span class=\"hl_operator\">∃ </span>z<span class=\"hl_operator\">.</span> (a++z) <span class=\"hl_operator\">=</span> b<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span>&quot;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;*/</span></p><br/>\n","title":"Multiset rewriting rules and restrictions"}